ACTRESS and radio host Khanyi Mbau’s daughter Khanukani is making her mum proud. The presenter who is known for going all out for her daughter a message on her Twitter page. This as she congratulated Khanukani over her academic achievements. Khanyi from Soweto fully supports her daughter. And Khanukani hasn't dissappointed her mum. Khanyi posted a lengthy message that read: “As a single mom , you have made the journey absolutely worth it @mbau2 thank you for being such an incredible daughter, walking this journey with you and your understanding in incredible… ... I love you Makhanz.” Khanyi's fans were excited while some of them received their final year results from varsities this month.